372
00:30:11.720 --> 00:30:14.420
<font color="#48D1CC">Itu sebabnya Presdir begitu menyukainya.

373
00:30:15.250 --> 00:30:16.380
<font color="#48D1CC">Ayah? Yoon Ha?

374
00:30:16.380 --> 00:30:19.090
<font color="#48D1CC">Terakhir kali, beliau marah karena hal-hal yang
