00:32:07.800 --> 00:32:09.980
<font color="#48D1CC">Apa maksudmu, "Aku mengerti. Pergilah"?

405
00:32:09.980 --> 00:32:14.800
<font color="#48D1CC">Jika kau bilang aku mengerti, itu berarti kau
